Karina Lewis murder?

700
00:27:09.774 --> 00:27:11.155
Yes.

701
00:27:11.155 --> 00:27:12.708
Your boyfriend at
the time. Ryan Jones.

702
00:27:12.708 --> 00:27:14.503
