that implicates Ryan.

717
00:27:46.811 --> 00:27:49.849
He said it--
it wasn't a big deal.

718
00:27:49.849 --> 00:27:52.955
He said that it would make
things easier if I just

719
00:27:52.955 --> 00:27:55.855
